data.description:
Rare Opportunity! 
Discover the perfect blend of style, space & convenience in this magnificent 2-story Trend home! 
Boasting 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, & a prime location, this stunning residence offers the ideal setting for any lifestyle.
The lower level features a spacious primary Bdrm with its own exit to the back yard ensuring privacy & comfort. The formal dining rm sets the stage for elegant meals, while the den provides the perfect space for a home office or study. Upstairs, a generous loft area offers endless possibilities for your hobbies, kids play room, or personal gym.
Each room generously sized, most with walk in closets! This home has been updated with a new HVAC system, new appliances & turf in both the back and front, giving the home exceptional curb appeal!
Welcome home!
